From phiscock at ee.ryerson.ca  Mon Apr  6 13:58:44 2015
From: phiscock at ee.ryerson.ca (phiscock at ee.ryerson.ca)
Date: Mon, 6 Apr 2015 09:58:44 -0400
Subject: [GTALUG] Linux on Canon camera
In-Reply-To: <5521C67C.8020501@gmail.com>
References: <d7c295640d817720d82604a900f6e5f7.squirrel@webmail.ee.ryerson.ca>
