From james.knott at rogers.com  Mon Apr  6 16:07:08 2015
From: james.knott at rogers.com (James Knott)
Date: Mon, 06 Apr 2015 12:07:08 -0400
Subject: [GTALUG] Where can I buy short ethernet and USB-to-microUSB
	cables?
In-Reply-To: <20150406190608.GB6612@waltdnes.org>
