FWIW, I have VirtualBox on my openSUSE 13.1 notebook.  I have installed
VMs for Windows 10, Windows 98 and OS/2 Warp 4.  I can switch among them
and back to Linux.  The VMs run full screen and to look at them, you
wouldn't know you were in a VM.

